'''圓展科技'''（AVer Information）為實物攝影機和[[視訊會議|視訊會議]]產品的製造商，總部位於[[台灣|台灣]][[新北市|新北市]][[土城區|土城區]]。圓展是[[台灣證券交易所|台灣證券交易所]][[上市公司|上市公司]]（{{twse|3669}}）、全球前三大實物攝影機製造商，2009年起在美國和西歐的市占率皆位居第一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tw.aver.com/press-release/142|title=圓展實物攝影機再創佳績，美國、西歐市佔率第一!|publisher=|accessdate=2011-09-19|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927113815/http://tw.aver.com/press-release/142|dead-url=no}}</ref>。旗下产品曾獲得包括德國iF產品設計獎和日本G-Mark優良設計獎等多个獎项<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.advanced-inc.com/2009/03/24/avermedia-picks-up-award-for-visualiser/|title=Advanced News - AverMedia picks up award for document camera|publisher=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425085513/http://news.advanced-inc.com/2009/03/24/avermedia-picks-up-award-for-visualiser/|archivedate=2012-04-25|accessdate=2011-09-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.averusa.com/business|title=Video Conferencing - AVer USA|publisher=|accessdate=2020-08-07|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213055345/https://www.averusa.com/business/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.red-dot.org/2786.html?&cHash=b4e5a70d60952f4ad6a3b354d8ca7f66&detail=5250|title=work - Red Dot Award: Product Design|website=en.red-dot.org|access-date=2011-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407061814/http://en.red-dot.org/2786.html?&cHash=b4e5a70d60952f4ad6a3b354d8ca7f66&detail=5250|archive-date=2012-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://tw.aver.com/awards|title=2015 獲獎消息│圓展科技|publisher=|accessdate=2011-09-19|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023214220/https://tw.aver.com/awards|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aver.com/press-release/AVerVision355AF-wins-2010-Worlddidac-Award|title=AVerVision355AF wins 2010 Worlddidac Award|publisher=|accessdate=2011-09-19|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927113848/http://www.aver.com/press-release/AVerVi